Formatting: Using format() to convert 145 into octal representation.

Area Calculation: Calculates the area of a circular pond with a radius of 84 meters and uses the formula π × r².

Bonus Calculation: Computes the total amount of water in the pond using a density of 1.4 liters per square meter.

Speed Calculation: Calculates the speed (in m/s) for crossing a 490-meter street in 7 minutes.

